<section class="section">
    <div class="r-container">
        <div class="d-flex flex-lg-row flex-column-reverse gap-3">
            <div class="col col-lg-12">
                <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-3">
                    <img src="~/img/community.jpg" alt="" class="img-fluid">
                    <p>
                        Community Day Services provide structured, meaningful activities that promote social inclusion, skill development, independence, and emotional wellbeing. Our day services give individuals the opportunity to engage with others, participate in enriching programmes, and enjoy a sense of purpose within a safe and welcoming community environment.

                    </p>
                    <br />
                    <p>
                        We offer a wide range of activities tailored to different interests and ability levels. These may include life-skills training, arts and crafts, digital skills, physical exercise, community outings, cooking sessions, confidence-building workshops, sensory activities, and social groups. Each programme is designed to enhance communication, build independence, strengthen relationships, and support personal development.

                    </p>
                    <br />
                    <p>
                        Our dedicated support workers encourage active participation, ensuring every individual feels heard, respected, and fully involved in choosing activities that reflect their preferences and aspirations. We also support individuals in accessing community resources such as libraries, leisure centres, volunteering opportunities, or local events—helping them build connections beyond the service.

                    </p>   <br />
                    <p>
                        Community Day Services play a vital role in preventing isolation, improving mental health, and enabling individuals to explore their interests in a structured yet flexible setting. Whether attending a few hours a week or full-time, each person receives purposeful support that enriches their daily life, builds confidence, and promotes overall wellbeing.

                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>